CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg. 12 reads: "Prothonotary - David B. Roberts, who, at 61, is completing his 16th year in office and seek a a fifth term. The office is one of the oldest under the Pennsylvania Constitution.  The Prothonotary is the elected Clerk of Common Pleas Court and ex-officio Clerk of the County court and Juvenile Court"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Prothonotary David B. Roberts, seated behind desk on office with television and pictures covering wall in background
